<center><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#333333" width="80%" bordercolor="#666666" style="border-left-width: 0; border-right-width: 0; border-bottom-width: 0; border-collapse:collapse"></center><tr><td align="left">
<font class="option" color="#ffffff"><b><a class="pn-title" href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=News&amp;file=article&amp;sid=33&amp;mode=thread&amp;order=0&amp;thold=0">Riftseekers Fun</a></b></font>
</td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
<font class="content"><div align="center">The Alliance headed over to Riftseekers Sanctum last night to take a stab at the zone, we ended up setting our sights o要 Feratha, after a few minutes of playing with the pull we engaged.<br><IMG alt=FerathaFight2.jpg src="http://img100.exs.cx/img100/1362/FerathaFight2.jpg"><br>After a few minutes, Feratha ended up dead to The Alliance, first try.<br><IMG alt=FerathaDead2.jpg src="http://img21.exs.cx/img21/1896/FerathaDead2.jpg"><br>As for loots, Grats Allayne o要 the two level 70 spell runes.Grats Zauber o要 <A href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=31643">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=31643</A>Thats it for now.<div><br><br>
</font>
