<font class="content">Posted by <a href="user.php?op=userinfo&amp;uname=Bumdbum">Bumdbum</a><br><b> on::</B> Oct 28, 2004 - 06:04 AM <b>(19 Reads)</b></font><br>
<font class="content">comments? <a class="pn-normal" href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=Recommend_Us&amp;file=index&amp;req=FriendSend&amp;sid=33"><img src="images/global/friend.gif" border="0" alt="Send this story to a friend"></a> <a class="pn-normal" href="print.php?sid=33"><img src="images/global/print.gif" border="0" alt="Printer friendly page"></a></font>
</td></tr></table>



</td></tr></table>


<br><br><br><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#333333" width="100%" bordercolor="#666666"
<tr><td>
<table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#333333" width="100%" bordercolor="#666666" <tr><td>
<center><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#333333" width="80%" bordercolor="#666666" style="border-left-width: 0; border-right-width: 0; border-bottom-width: 0; border-collapse:collapse"></center><tr><td align="left">
<font class="option" color="#ffffff"><b><a class="pn-title" href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=News&amp;file=article&amp;sid=31&amp;mode=thread&amp;order=0&amp;thold=0">Bartx Drops his Pants!</a></b></font>
</td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
<font class="content"><P align=center><FONT face=Arial>We came, we saw we conqured.<BR>We learned from previous mistakes, and I saw what truely amazed me.....<BR></FONT><FONT ><U><FONT face=Arial color=lawngreen><FONT  color=deeppink>HARDLY ANYONE WENT AFK!</FONT><BR></FONT></U><FONT ><FONT face=Arial>We proudly present to you<BR></FONT><BR><A href="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/Uqua/readytostrike.jpg" target=_blank><IMG alt="Click here to see the full sized pic" src="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/Uqua/smallreadytostrike.jpg" border=0></A><BR><BR>We had that feeling, we knew we were going to win.  Everything had gone right..<BR><BR><A href="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/Uqua/blastdead.jpg" target=_blank><IMG alt="Click here to see the full sized pic" src="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/Uqua/smallblastdead.jpg" border=0></FONT></FONT></A><BR><BR>I had to use that pic, it shows Finny didnt run fast enough!<BR>A better group shot though<BR><BR><A href="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/Uqua/deadbarxt..jpg" target=_blank><IMG alt="Click here to see the full sized pic" src="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/Uqua/smalldeadbarxt..jpg" border=0></A><BR><BR>Our just rewards? Getting to see another look alike GoD model that gave us flags! <BR>We all love flags so much don't we?<BR><BR><A href="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/Uqua/barxtspect.jpg" target=_blank><IMG alt="Click here to see the full sized pic" src="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/Uqua/smallbarxtspect.jpg" border=0></A><BR><BR>Drops included <A href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=68748">Ceremonial Jade-Inlaid Cuirass</A> and <A href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=68752">Bone Mask of Shadows</A><BR>Construct also dropped <A href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=68753">Polished Ceremonial Mask</A><BR><BR>Grats Riji and Pheobe o要 BPs, Galolron o要 Bone Mask, and Klaget o要 Polished Mask!<BR>Great job guys!<BR><BR>Don't let me forget to mention the the Alliance is currently accepting applicants, refer to <BR><A href="http://www.shardsofavalon.com/index.php?name=PNphpBB2&amp;file=viewtopic&amp;t=814">THIS POST</A> for more information.  <BR><BR>Also for alliance members remeber to update your <A href="http://www.shardsofavalon.com/index.php?module=character_edit&amp;func=main">GoD Flags</A><BR></P><br><br>
</font>
</td></tr></table>
