<font class="content"><P align=center>Guess I should get back o要 top of things eh?Well we have been playing around a lot in Gates of Discord, and let me tell you it frikin sucks, unless of course you like being hit for over 3,000 damage.  I have not been o要e rounded in months, until we stumbled into Ikkiniz 4, when the good ole Keeper of the Altar summoned me and pummeled me with tripple 3ks! <STRONG>&lt;OUCH&gt;</STRONG>Anyway, no matter how hard he hits, he hit the ground just that hard too!<IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/keeperdead.jpg" align=baseline border=0>So since then we have been playing around in Uqua and that place is even worse!Note sorry to say it Exec but I'm glad you're not around for this raid! &lt;Smile Love ya buddy&gt;We have been doing fairly well, progress has been quick, but far from smooth, tempers flare people get upset with each other, but what does that do? Make us work harder to make the other guy appear wrong! &lt;MWAHAHA&gt;  Anyway I've been getting some really horrible screenshots, if someone has some good o要es feel free to drop them in the picture gallery and Ill make some more updates!Until next time</P>
<br><br>
